data.description: Unique opportunity! Over 2,000 sq ft home offers five bedrooms, three bathrooms sits on a large corner lot along with a detached 2 car garage, an outbuilding for additional storage and several livestock pens. This home can be utilized as a single-family residence or easily converted into two separate living areas for multi-generational use, more than one family, as an investment property or even convert into two units, rent out one and live in the other, the possibilities are endless! The second story is accessible separately from the first level, has its own heating and cooling source, and is fully plumbed for a kitchen and a laundry room. Schedule a showing with your favorite realtor today!
